'''Nana Kofi Obonyaa''' (born 7 January 1920) awo din Roland James Moxon, bɛyɛɛ obroni fitaa a wɔ dinkan yɛɛ ohene wɔ Ankobea mpotɛmu a ɛwɔ Aburi wɔ afe 1963.Na wɔ dee dwuma pii wɔ ahensem mu paa.Na ɔyɛ adwuma ma mmrɔfo a wɔ dii yɛnso no,mmrɔfo aban mu dwumayɛnii ,Odikro ,twerɛtwerɛfoɔ.

== Abakɔsem ==
Kofi Obonyaa baa Ghana ɛnkani Gold Coast(Sika mpoano) abrɛ a na ɛwiase nyina reko mprɛno so no  "World War II" sɛ abrofo aban dwumayɛnii.wɔ wo no wɔ Shrewsbury ɛna wɔ kɔɔ sukuu wɔ Denstone.wɔ san kɔ sua abakɔsem wɔ St. Johns Sukuu wɔ Cambridge.

AbrƐ a ntɔkwa no seeɛ no wɔ ba Ghana bɛyɛɛ mpotɛmu wɔ Dodowa,aburi,Kpando ne Nkran.Ghana nyaa mfahodeɛ no ,Ghana man panin Dr.Kwame Nkrumah ma no bɛyɛɛ ne futofoɔ.Moxon ndwuma a wɔ bɛyɛɛ no bi ne Ghana Cine dwumakuo.Nana ne yonko ne Edgar F.Kaiser a wɔ bua mmaa Ghana tuu mpon.Moxon toaso kɔ boa wɔ Volta River Authority ma wɔn sii Akosombo Dam.

Na wɔ tu kwan kɔ Britian baako pɛ wɔ afe biara mu ,yei kyeresɛ na wɔ tena Ghana paa.

Afe 1963 wɔ kɔɔ ahomigyeɛ mu abrɛ nu mo na won si ne hene ma nu abodin Nana Kofi Obonyaa din no kyerɛsɛ wɔ wu no ɛfieda wɔ nsanieɛ ase.

Abakosɛm kyerɛ sɛ w'anware nanso wɔ gye nnipa bebreee ne won tenaeɛ.

Na wɔ gye ahohoɔ a na wɔ ba abibiman mu ɛsansaa nti wɔ frɛ no Obroni fitaa odikro.


